snippet.title: New content and raid event in Warhammer Skulls update!
snippet.description:
Sharpen your axes and ready your bolters, the time for the harvest of skulls is here! This year Warhammer SKULLS brings a trove of new content and amazing deals, including a new raid event, new Battle Pass, and a DLC featuring Angron himself! Check out the details in the latest blog post:
https://www.horusheresylegions.com/warhammer-skulls-2023

Prepare to enter the fray and sate Khorne's hunger for war! Get ready to fight in The Conqueror's raid event to unlock a terrifying new Warlord, collect exclusive cosmetics with the new Battle Pass and complete your collection with some of the most red-handed warriors in the Galaxy. 

#horuslegions #warhammer #warhammer40k #horusheresy #warhammer30k #30k #wh40k #40k #WarhammerSkulls

Skulls for the Skull Throne! 👇
